      • isWhiteList

        public boolean isWhiteList()
        Check if the filter whitelists or blacklists items. A whitelist filter allows only the items added to it to pass; a blacklist filter allows any items except the items added to it to pass.
        Returns:
        true if this filter whitelists; false if it blacklists
